 standard pricing on a 4GB KVM VPS hosted at their datacenter in The Netherlands. VPSSlim has been featured on LowEndBox a <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/?s=vpsslim&amp;searchsubmit=Find\">number of times over the past decade</a> and if you are looking for some nostalgia <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/vpsslim-e17-88yearly-23-256mb-openvz-vps-in-netherlands/\">check out their offer from 2012</a>. VPSSlim has been in business for approximately ten years, so they can be trusted to provide a reliable customer experience, and for that reason we are designating them a \u201cResident Host\u201d here on LowEndBox.</p><p>Their WHOIS is public and you can find their <a href=\"https://www.hostslim.eu/assets/termsofservice.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ToS/Legal Docs</a> on their website. They accept PayPal. Bitcoin, iDeal, Credit cards and Wire as payment methods.</p><p>See the plans below and should you order, use the promo code <strong>LEBKVMJUNE</strong> for 70% off and please feel free to comment below and tell us of your experience!</p><p><strong>Here\u2019s what they had to say:&nbsp;</strong></p><p><em>\u201cVPSslim offers a wide range of virtual server solutions and was founded in 2009. Over the past 10 years we have grown into one of the larger hosting providers in the Netherlands. We have a tight partnership with Alticom datacenters where we operate our own floor/ datacenter. We own and operate all our equipment, hardware, routing &amp; switching. We have in-house engineers that are available 24/7 for any of your support needs. Our floor is redundant in both power, aggregate, UPS as well as fiber and network peering partners. When you join VPSslim you are instantly connected to a global premium network of over 1.2 Tbps. Enjoy your endless hosting needs in our incredible wide network, while at the same time benefiting from effective DDoS protection.\u201d</em></p><p><strong>Here\u2019s the offer:&nbsp;</strong></p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>VPS 4GB KVM</b></p><ul><li><div>2x Intel Xeon CPU</div></li><li><div>4096 MB RAM</div><div></div></li><li><div>4096 MB SWAP</div></li><li><div>2x vCPU</div></li><li><div>150GB HDD space</div></li><li><div>5TB transfer</div></li><li><div>1Gbps uplink</div></li><li><div>1x IPv4</div></li><li><div>/64 IPv6</div></li><li><div>KVM/SolusVM</div></li><li><div>Coupon: LEBKVMJUNE</div></li><li><div>$7/month</div></li><li>[<a href=\"https://www.vpsslim.com/cp/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=5&amp;promocode=LEBKVMJUNE\">ORDER HERE</a>]</li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"></td><td valign=\"top\"></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Check out their network information and node specs after the break.</p><p>And please leave feedback in the comments below!<br>\n<span id=\"more-23848\"></span><br>\n<strong>NETWORK INFO:</strong></p><p>HostSlim Datacenter Lelystad<br>\nTest IPv4:&nbsp;103.214.7.250<br>\nTest IPv6:&nbsp;2a06:5b80:1::893c:63a<br>\nTest file:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://lg.hostslim.nl/LookingGlass/1000MB.test\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">1000MB</a><br>\nLooking glass:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://lg.hostslim.nl/LookingGlass/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://lg.hostslim.nl/LookingGlass/</a></p><p><b>Host Nodes:</b></p><p>\u2013 2x Intel Xeon E5-2620 CPU<br>\n\u2013 256GB RAM<br>\n\u2013 4x 8TB HDDs<br>\n\u2013 Hardware RAID10<br>\n\u2013 10Gbps uplink</p><p>Please let us know if you have any questions/comments and enjoy!</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A